<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Personal Tax Services - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>

    <section class="page-header page-header-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Personal Tax Services</h1>
        <p>Tailored tax planning, filing, and advisory to protect and optimize your personal wealth.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-detail services-page">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="services-grid" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">

          <!-- Partnership Accounts -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-users-gear"></i></div>
              <h2>Partnership Accounts</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Ensure clear compliance and precise profit distribution across your business partnership. We manage the
                complexities of joint filing and partnership taxation rules under HMRC.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Preparation of Partnership Financial Statements</li>
                <li>Partnership Tax Return (SA800) filing with HMRC</li>
                <li>Allocation of profits/losses and Partner Capital accounts</li>
                <li>Individual Partner tax computation advisory</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Sole Traders Acc -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></div>
              <h2>Sole Traders Acc</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Running a solo business in London can be demanding. We take the stress out of accounting, bookkeeping,
                and Self Assessment filings, letting you focus on delivering to your client.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Annual Sole Trader accounts preperaion</li>
                <li>HMRC Self Assessment tax return (SA100)</li>
                <li>Expense optimization & allowable deductions check</li>
                <li>Proactive national insurance (Class 2 & 4) planning</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Property Rental Acc -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-house-chimney-user"></i></div>
              <h2>Property Rental Acc</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Maximise the returns from your property investments. Whether you hold a single buy-to-let property or a
                diverse portfolio, we navigate complex UK property tax rules for you.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Property income and expense statements</li>
                <li>Advice on mortgage interest relief restrictions (Section 24)</li>
                <li>Capital Gains Tax (CGT) declarations & reporting</li>
                <li>Non-Resident Landlord scheme compliance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Locum Acc -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-doctor"></i></div>
              <h2>Locum Acc</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Healthcare professionals, locum doctors, and dental practitioners face unique invoicing, shift
                structures, and pension rules. We keep your accounts structured and aligned.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Locum invoicing and mileage tracking support</li>
                <li>NHS Pension scheme income reconciliation</li>
                <li>Locum-specific allowable expense management</li>
                <li>Self assessment filing and payment reminder schedule</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Looking for Personal Tax Guidance?</h2>
        <p>Let's map out your tax efficiency in a free consultation call.</p>
        <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Call</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>

</html>